ArtsBeat: ‘Star Wars: The Force Awakens’ Trailer Is Set to Debut, and Tickets Will Go On Sale 
Published By: NYTimes - Today 
Tickets for “Star Wars: The Force Awakens” will be available on Monday evening after the broadcast of the first full trailer....
